w on brand!\", \"from\": 3292, \"to\": 3404, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She really does just wanna have some fun, yawl.'\", \"from\": 3405, \"to\": 3453, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Got a story?\", \"from\": 3455, \"to\": 3467, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you have got a celebrity story, video or pictures get in touch with theMetro.co.ukentertainment team by emailing us celebtips@metro.co.uk, calling 020 3615 2145 or by visiting ourSubmit Stuffpage - we'd love to hear from you.\", \"from\": 3469, \"to\": 3697, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Noah Lyles' mum blasts Paris Olympics for leaving son with covid 'gasping for air' after race  ArrowMORE:Tom Daley announces retirement from diving following Paris Olympics  ArrowMORE:Most memorable and controversial moments of the Paris Olympics after a wild ride in the French capital\", \"from\": 3699, \"to\": 3995, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3709, \"end\": 3719, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}, {\"begin\": 3814, \"end\": 3823, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.110303057632317e-36, \"text\": \"Tom Daley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\"}, {\"begin\": 3981, \"end\": 3987, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9963155724350563, \"rank\": 0.003502805639081862, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}]}"